## Result: replay plateaus above 10k
[[Result: replay plateaus above 10k]]
>>id: lp_lab00000011
>>type: result
>>finding: forgetting climbs to 18% at 10k classes regardless of buffer size
>>contradicts: [[Replay prevents forgetting]]

[[Result: replay plateaus above 10k]] →(derived-from) [[EXP-047 replay at 10k classes]]
[[Result: replay plateaus above 10k]] →(contradicts) [[Replay prevents forgetting]]
[[Result: replay plateaus above 10k]] →(raises) [[Why does replay plateau?]]

